input.activity_signal: Recent FCC filing (2024-10-11) for VoIP numbering authorization. input.product_summary: TDS Metrocom is a local phone service provider offering voice, data, and Internet services in the midwestern United States, operating as part of TDS Telecom's telecommunications infrastructure with VoIP capabilities through PSTN interconnection.
